\par \'93What fault did your forefathers find in me,
\par So that they strayed so far from me,
\par And they walked after worthless idols and became worthless themselves?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af25 \ltrch\fcs0 \f1\cf23\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033\langfenp1033\insrsid9976433 6}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af25 \ltrch\fcs0 \f1\cf25\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033\langfenp1033\insrsid9976433 \~They did not ask, \lquote Where is Jehovah,
\par The One who brought us out of the land of Egypt,
\par Who led us through the wilderness,
\par Through a land of deserts and pits,
\par Through a land of drought and of deep shadow,
\par Through a land where no man travels
\par And where no humans dwell?\rquote 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af25 \ltrch\fcs0 \f1\cf23\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033\langfenp1033\insrsid9976433 7}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af25 \ltrch\fcs0 \f1\cf25\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033\langfenp1033\insrsid9976433 \~I then brought you to a land of orchards,
