\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af25 \ltrch\fcs0 \f1\cf23\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033\langfenp1033\insrsid9976433 8}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af25 \ltrch\fcs0 \f1\cf25\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033\langfenp1033\insrsid9976433 \~The priests did not ask, \lquote Where is Jehovah?
\rquote 
\par Those handling the Law did not know me,
\par The shepherds rebelled against me,
\par The prophets prophesied by Ba\u697\'5fal,
\par And they followed those who could bring no benefit.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af25 \ltrch\fcs0 \f1\cf23\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033\langfenp1033\insrsid9976433 9}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af25 \ltrch\fcs0 \f1\cf25\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033\langfenp1033\insrsid9976433 \~\lquote So I will contend further with you,\rquote 
 declares Jehovah,
\par \lquote And I will contend with the sons of your sons.\rquote 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af25 \ltrch\fcs0 \f1\cf23\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033\langfenp1033\insrsid9976433 10}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af25 \ltrch\fcs0 \f1\cf25\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033\langfenp1033\insrsid9976433 \~\lquote But cross over to the coastlands of the Kit
\u697\'5ftim and see.
