\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af25 \ltrch\fcs0 \f1\cf23\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033\langfenp1033\insrsid9976433 17}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af25 \ltrch\fcs0 \f1\cf25\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033\langfenp1033\insrsid9976433 \~Have you not brought this on yourself
