\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af25 \ltrch\fcs0 \f1\cf23\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033\langfenp1033\insrsid9976433 19}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af25 \ltrch\fcs0 \f1\cf25\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033\langfenp1033\insrsid9976433 \~Your wickedness should correct you,
\par And your own unfaithfulness should reprove you.
\par Know and realize how bad and bitter it is
\par To abandon Jehovah your God;
\par You have shown no fear of me,\rquote  declares the Sovereign Lord, Jehovah of armies.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af25 \ltrch\fcs0 \f1\cf23\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033\langfenp1033\insrsid9976433 20}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af25 \ltrch\fcs0 \f1\cf25\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033\langfenp1033\insrsid9976433 \~\lquote For long ago I smashed your yoke
\par And tore off your shackles.
\par But you said: \'93I am not going to serve,\'94
\par For on every high hill and under every luxuriant tree
\par You were lying sprawled out, prostituting yourself.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af25 \ltrch\fcs0 \f1\cf23\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033\langfenp1033\insrsid9976433 21}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af25 \ltrch\fcs0 \f1\cf25\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033\langfenp1033\insrsid9976433 \~
I planted you as a choice red vine, all of it pure seed;
\par So how have you turned into the degenerate shoots of a foreign vine before me?\rquote 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af25 \ltrch\fcs0 \f1\cf23\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033\langfenp1033\insrsid9976433 22}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af25 \ltrch\fcs0 \f1\cf25\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033\langfenp1033\insrsid9976433 \~\lquote 
Though you should wash with soda and use much lye,
\par Your guilt would still be a stain before me,\rquote  declares the Sovereign Lord Jehovah.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af25 \ltrch\fcs0 \f1\cf23\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033\langfenp1033\insrsid9976433 23}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af25 \ltrch\fcs0 \f1\cf25\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033\langfenp1033\insrsid9976433 \~How can you say, \lquote I have not defiled myself.

\par I have not followed the Ba\u697\'5fals\rquote ?
\par Look at your way in the valley.
\par Consider what you have done.
\par You are like a swift, young she-camel,
\par Aimlessly running back and forth in her ways,
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af25 \ltrch\fcs0 \f1\cf23\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033\langfenp1033\insrsid9976433 24}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af25 \ltrch\fcs0 \f1\cf25\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033\langfenp1033\insrsid9976433 \~A wild donkey accustomed to the wilderness,
