\par But you said, \lquote It is hopeless!
\par No! I have fallen in love with strangers,
\par And I will follow them.\rquote 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af25 \ltrch\fcs0 \f1\cf23\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033\langfenp1033\insrsid9976433 26}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af25 \ltrch\fcs0 \f1\cf25\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033\langfenp1033\insrsid9976433 \~Like the shame of a thief when he is caught,
\par So the house of Israel has been put to shame,
\par They, their kings and their princes,
