\par Because the nations are terrified by them.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af25 \ltrch\fcs0 \f1\cf23\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033\langfenp1033\insrsid9976433 3}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af25 \ltrch\fcs0 \f1\cf25\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033\langfenp1033\insrsid9976433 \~For the customs of the peoples are a delusion.

