\par Their clothing is blue thread and purple wool.
\par They are all made by skilled workers.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af25 \ltrch\fcs0 \f1\cf23\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033\langfenp1033\insrsid9976433 10}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af25 \ltrch\fcs0 \f1\cf25\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033\langfenp1033\insrsid9976433 \~But Jehovah is truly God.
