\par And I answered: \'93Amen, O Jehovah.\'94
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af25 \ltrch\fcs0 \f1\cf23\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033\langfenp1033\insrsid9976433 6}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af25 \ltrch\fcs0 \f1\cf24\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033\langfenp1033\insrsid9976433 \~Jehovah then said to me: \'93
