\af25 \ltrch\fcs0 \f1\cf6\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033\langfenp1033\insrsid9976433 ra}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af25 \ltrch\fcs0 \f1\cf25\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033\langfenp1033\insrsid9976433 tha\u697\'5fim and against the inhabitants of Pe\u697\'5fkod.
\par Let them be massacred and completely destroyed,\'94 declares Jehovah.
\par \'93Do all that I have commanded you.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af25 \ltrch\fcs0 \f1\cf23\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033\langfenp1033\insrsid9976433 22}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af25 \ltrch\fcs0 \f1\cf25\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033\langfenp1033\insrsid9976433 \~There is the sound of war in the land,
\par A great catastrophe.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af25 \ltrch\fcs0 \f1\cf23\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033\langfenp1033\insrsid9976433 23}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af25 \ltrch\fcs0 \f1\cf25\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033\langfenp1033\insrsid9976433 \~
How the forge hammer of all the earth has been cut down and broken!
\par How Babylon has become an object of horror among the nations!
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af25 \ltrch\fcs0 \f1\cf23\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033\langfenp1033\insrsid9976433 24}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af25 \ltrch\fcs0 \f1\cf25\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033\langfenp1033\insrsid9976433 \~
I have laid a snare for you, and you have been caught, O Babylon,
\par And you did not know it.
\par You were found and captured,
\par For it was Jehovah whom you opposed.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af25 \ltrch\fcs0 \f1\cf23\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033\langfenp1033\insrsid9976433 25}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af25 \ltrch\fcs0 \f1\cf25\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033\langfenp1033\insrsid9976433 \~Jehovah has opened his storehouse,
\par And he brings out the weapons of his indignation.
\par For the Sovereign Lord, Jehovah of armies, has a work
\par In the land of the Cha}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af25 \ltrch\fcs0 \f1\cf6\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033\langfenp1033\insrsid9976433 l}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af25 \ltrch\fcs0 \f1\cf25\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033\langfenp1033\insrsid9976433 de\u697\'5fans.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af25 \ltrch\fcs0 \f1\cf23\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033\langfenp1033\insrsid9976433 26}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af25 \ltrch\fcs0 \f1\cf25\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033\langfenp1033\insrsid9976433 \~Come against her from distant places.
\par Open up her granaries.
\par Pile her up like heaps of grain.
\par Destroy her completely.
\par May she have no one left.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af25 \ltrch\fcs0 \f1\cf23\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033\langfenp1033\insrsid9976433 27}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af25 \ltrch\fcs0 \f1\cf25\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033\langfenp1033\insrsid9976433 \~Massacre all her young bulls;
\par Let them go down to the slaughter.
\par Woe to them, for their day has come,
\par Their time of reckoning!
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af25 \ltrch\fcs0 \f1\cf23\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033\langfenp1033\insrsid9976433 28}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af25 \ltrch\fcs0 \f1\cf25\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033\langfenp1033\insrsid9976433 \~There is the sound of those fleeing,
\par Those escaping from the land of Babylon,
\par To declare in Zion the vengeance of Jehovah our God,
\par The vengeance for his temple.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af25 \ltrch\fcs0 \f1\cf23\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033\langfenp1033\insrsid9976433 29}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af25 \ltrch\fcs0 \f1\cf25\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033\langfenp1033\insrsid9976433 \~Summon archers against Babylon,
\par All who are bending the bow.
\par Camp all around her; let no one escape.
\par Repay her according to her activity.
\par Do to her just as she has done.
\par For she has acted arrogantly against Jehovah,
\par Against the Holy One of Israel.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af25 \ltrch\fcs0 \f1\cf23\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033\langfenp1033\insrsid9976433 30}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af25 \ltrch\fcs0 \f1\cf25\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033\langfenp1033\insrsid9976433 \~So her young men will fall in her public squares,

\par And all her soldiers will perish in that day,\'94 declares Jehovah.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af25 \ltrch\fcs0 \f1\cf23\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033\langfenp1033\insrsid9976433 31}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af25 \ltrch\fcs0 \f1\cf25\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033\langfenp1033\insrsid9976433 \~\'93Look! I am against you, O defiant one,\'94
 declares the Sovereign Lord, Jehovah of armies,
\par \'93For your day must come, the time that I will call you to account.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af25 \ltrch\fcs0 \f1\cf23\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033\langfenp1033\insrsid9976433 32}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af25 \ltrch\fcs0 \f1\cf25\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033\langfenp1033\insrsid9976433 \~You, O defiant one, will stumble and fall,
\par With no one to raise you up.
\par And I will set your cities on fire,
\par And it will consume everything around you.\'94
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af25 \ltrch\fcs0 \f1\cf23\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033\langfenp1033\insrsid9976433 33}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af25 \ltrch\fcs0 \f1\cf25\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033\langfenp1033\insrsid9976433 \~This is what Jehovah of armies says:
\par \'93The people of Israel and Judah are oppressed,
\par And all those taking them captive have held onto them.
\par They have refused to let them go.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af25 \ltrch\fcs0 \f1\cf23\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033\langfenp1033\insrsid9976433 34}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af25 \ltrch\fcs0 \f1\cf25\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033\langfenp1033\insrsid9976433 \~But their Repurchaser is strong.
\par Jehovah of armies is his name.
\par He will surely plead their legal case,
\par In order to give rest to the land
\par And to bring agitation to the inhabitants of Babylon.\'94
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af25 \ltrch\fcs0 \f1\cf23\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033\langfenp1033\insrsid9976433 35}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af25 \ltrch\fcs0 \f1\cf25\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033\langfenp1033\insrsid9976433 \~\'93There is a sword against the Cha}{\rtlch\fcs1 
\af25 \ltrch\fcs0 \f1\cf6\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033\langfenp1033\insrsid9976433 l}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af25 \ltrch\fcs0 \f1\cf25\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033\langfenp1033\insrsid9976433 de\u697\'5fans,\'94 declares Jehovah,
\par \'93Against the inhabitants of Babylon and against her princes and against her wise ones.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af25 \ltrch\fcs0 \f1\cf23\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033\langfenp1033\insrsid9976433 36}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af25 \ltrch\fcs0 \f1\cf25\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033\langfenp1033\insrsid9976433 \~There is a sword again
st the empty talkers, and they will act foolishly.
\par There is a sword against her warriors, and they will become terrified.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af25 \ltrch\fcs0 \f1\cf23\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033\langfenp1033\insrsid9976433 37}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af25 \ltrch\fcs0 \f1\cf25\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033\langfenp1033\insrsid9976433 \~
There is a sword against their horses and their war chariots,
\par And against all the mixed populations in her midst,
\par And they will become like women.
\par There is a sword against her treasures, and they will be plundered.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af25 \ltrch\fcs0 \f1\cf23\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033\langfenp1033\insrsid9976433 38}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af25 \ltrch\fcs0 \f1\cf25\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033\langfenp1033\insrsid9976433 \~
There is a devastation on her waters, and they will be dried up.
\par For it is a land of graven images,
\par And because of their frightful visions they keep acting with madness.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af25 \ltrch\fcs0 \f1\cf23\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033\langfenp1033\insrsid9976433 39}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af25 \ltrch\fcs0 \f1\cf25\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033\langfenp1033\insrsid9976433 \~
Therefore, the desert creatures will dwell with the howling animals,
\par And in her the ostriches will dwell.
\par She will never again be inhabited,
\par Nor will she be a place of residence throughout all generations.\'94
\par }\pard \ltrpar\ql \fi576\li0\ri0\nowidctlpar\wrapdefault\faauto\rin0\lin0\itap0 {\rtlch\fcs1 \af25 \ltrch\fcs0 \f1\cf23\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033\langfenp1033\insrsid9976433 40}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af25 \ltrch\fcs0 
