\par }\pard \ltrpar\ql \fi-432\li432\ri0\nowidctlpar\wrapdefault\faauto\rin0\lin432\itap0 {\rtlch\fcs1 \af25 \ltrch\fcs0 \f1\cf23\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033\langfenp1033\insrsid9976433 41}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af25 \ltrch\fcs0 
\f1\cf25\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033\langfenp1033\insrsid9976433 \~Look! A people is coming in from the north;
\par A great nation and grand kings will be raised up
\par From the remotest parts of the earth.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af25 \ltrch\fcs0 \f1\cf23\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033\langfenp1033\insrsid9976433 42}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af25 \ltrch\fcs0 \f1\cf25\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033\langfenp1033\insrsid9976433 \~Bow and javelin they wield.
\par They are cruel and will show no mercy.
\par Their sound is like the roaring sea,
\par As they ride on their horses.
\par Like one man, they line up in battle formation against you, O daughter of Babylon.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af25 \ltrch\fcs0 \f1\cf23\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033\langfenp1033\insrsid9976433 43}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af25 \ltrch\fcs0 \f1\cf25\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033\langfenp1033\insrsid9976433 \~
The king of Babylon has heard the report about them,
\par And his hands drop down.
\par Anguish seizes him,
\par Pain like that of a woman giving birth.
\par }\pard \ltrpar\ql \fi576\li0\ri0\nowidctlpar\wrapdefault\faauto\rin0\lin0\itap0 {\rtlch\fcs1 \af25 \ltrch\fcs0 \f1\cf23\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033\langfenp1033\insrsid9976433 44}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af25 \ltrch\fcs0 
