secure pastures like a lion from the dense thickets along the Jordan, but in a moment I will make them run away from her. And I will appoint over her the chosen one. For who is like me, and who will challenge me? What shepherd can stand before me? }{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af25 \ltrch\fcs0 \f1\cf23\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033\langfenp1033\insrsid9976433 45}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af25 \ltrch\fcs0 \f1\cf24\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033\langfenp1033\insrsid9976433 \~There
fore hear, O men, the decision that Jehovah has made against Babylon and what he has thought out against the land of the Cha}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af25 \ltrch\fcs0 \f1\cf6\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033\langfenp1033\insrsid9976433 l}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af25 
\ltrch\fcs0 \f1\cf24\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033\langfenp1033\insrsid9976433 de\u697\'5fans.
\par }\pard \ltrpar\ql \fi-432\li432\ri0\nowidctlpar\wrapdefault\faauto\rin0\lin432\itap0 {\rtlch\fcs1 \af25 \ltrch\fcs0 \f1\cf25\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033\langfenp1033\insrsid9976433 Surely the little ones of the flock will be dragged away.
\par He will make their dwelling place desolate because of them.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af25 \ltrch\fcs0 \f1\cf23\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033\langfenp1033\insrsid9976433 46}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af25 \ltrch\fcs0 \f1\cf25\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033\langfenp1033\insrsid9976433 \~At the sound of Babylon\rquote 
