\par And an outcry will be heard among the nations.\'94
\par }\pard \ltrpar\qc \fi576\li0\ri0\nowidctlpar\wrapdefault\faauto\rin0\lin0\itap0 {\rtlch\fcs1 \af25 \ltrch\fcs0 \b\fs32\cf21\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033\langfenp1033\insrsid9976433 Chapter }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af25 \ltrch\fcs0 
