\f1\cf25\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033\langfenp1033\insrsid9976433 \~This is what Jehovah says:
\par \'93Here I am raising up a destructive wind
\par Against Babylon and the inhabitants of Leb-ka\u697\'5fmai.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af25 \ltrch\fcs0 \f1\cf23\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033\langfenp1033\insrsid9976433 2}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af25 \ltrch\fcs0 \f1\cf25\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033\langfenp1033\insrsid9976433 \~I will send winnowers to Babylon,
\par And they will winnow her and make her land empty;
\par They will come against her on all sides in the day of calamity.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af25 \ltrch\fcs0 \f1\cf23\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033\langfenp1033\insrsid9976433 3}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af25 \ltrch\fcs0 \f1\cf25\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033\langfenp1033\insrsid9976433 \~Let the archer not bend his bow.
\par And let no one stand up in his coat of mail.
\par Show no compassion for her young men.
\par Devote all her army to destruction.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af25 \ltrch\fcs0 \f1\cf23\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033\langfenp1033\insrsid9976433 4}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af25 \ltrch\fcs0 \f1\cf25\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033\langfenp1033\insrsid9976433 \~And they will fall slain in the land of the Cha}{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af25 \ltrch\fcs0 \f1\cf6\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033\langfenp1033\insrsid9976433 l}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af25 \ltrch\fcs0 \f1\cf25\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033\langfenp1033\insrsid9976433 de\u697\'5fans,
\par Pierced through in her streets.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af25 \ltrch\fcs0 \f1\cf23\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033\langfenp1033\insrsid9976433 5}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af25 \ltrch\fcs0 \f1\cf25\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033\langfenp1033\insrsid9976433 \~
For Israel and Judah are not widowed from their God, from Jehovah of armies.
\par But their land is full of guilt from the standpoint of the Holy One of Israel.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af25 \ltrch\fcs0 \f1\cf23\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033\langfenp1033\insrsid9976433 6}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af25 \ltrch\fcs0 \f1\cf25\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033\langfenp1033\insrsid9976433 \~Flee out of the midst of Babylon,
\par And escape for your life.
\par Do not perish because of her error.
\par For it is the time for Jehovah\rquote s vengeance.
\par He is paying her back for what she has done.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af25 \ltrch\fcs0 \f1\cf23\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033\langfenp1033\insrsid9976433 7}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af25 \ltrch\fcs0 \f1\cf25\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033\langfenp1033\insrsid9976433 \~
Babylon has been a golden cup in the hand of Jehovah;
\par She made all the earth drunk.
\par From her wine the nations have drunk;
\par That is why the nations have gone mad.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af25 \ltrch\fcs0 \f1\cf23\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033\langfenp1033\insrsid9976433 8}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af25 \ltrch\fcs0 \f1\cf25\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033\langfenp1033\insrsid9976433 \~Suddenly Babylon has fallen and is broken.
\par Wail over her!
\par Get balsam for her pain; perhaps she may be healed.\'94
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af25 \ltrch\fcs0 \f1\cf23\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033\langfenp1033\insrsid9976433 9}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af25 \ltrch\fcs0 \f1\cf25\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033\langfenp1033\insrsid9976433 \~\'93
We tried to heal Babylon, but she could not be healed.
\par Leave her and let us go, each to his own land.
\par For her judgment has reached to the heavens;
\par It is as high as the clouds.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af25 \ltrch\fcs0 \f1\cf23\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033\langfenp1033\insrsid9976433 10}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af25 \ltrch\fcs0 \f1\cf25\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033\langfenp1033\insrsid9976433 \~Jehovah has brought about justice for us.
\par Come, let us recount in Zion the work of Jehovah our God.\'94
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af25 \ltrch\fcs0 \f1\cf23\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033\langfenp1033\insrsid9976433 11}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af25 \ltrch\fcs0 \f1\cf25\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033\langfenp1033\insrsid9976433 \~\'93
Polish the arrows; take up the circular shields.
\par Jehovah has stirred up the spirit of the kings of the Medes,
\par Because he intends to bring Babylon to ruin.
\par For this is the vengeance of Jehovah, the vengeance for his temple.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af25 \ltrch\fcs0 \f1\cf23\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033\langfenp1033\insrsid9976433 12}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af25 \ltrch\fcs0 \f1\cf25\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033\langfenp1033\insrsid9976433 \~Lift up a signal against the walls of Babylon.

\par Strengthen the guard, post the watchmen.
\par Prepare those in ambush.
\par For Jehovah has devised the strategy,
\par And he will carry out what he has promised against the inhabitants of Babylon.\'94
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af25 \ltrch\fcs0 \f1\cf23\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033\langfenp1033\insrsid9976433 13}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af25 \ltrch\fcs0 \f1\cf25\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033\langfenp1033\insrsid9976433 \~\'93O woman who resides on many waters,
\par With abundant treasures,
\par Your end has come, the limit of your profit-making.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af25 \ltrch\fcs0 \f1\cf23\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033\langfenp1033\insrsid9976433 14}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af25 \ltrch\fcs0 \f1\cf25\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033\langfenp1033\insrsid9976433 \~Jehovah of armies has sworn by himself,
\par \lquote I will fill you with men, as numerous as locusts,
\par And they will shout in triumph over you.\rquote 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af25 \ltrch\fcs0 \f1\cf23\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033\langfenp1033\insrsid9976433 15}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af25 \ltrch\fcs0 \f1\cf25\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033\langfenp1033\insrsid9976433 \~He is the Maker of the earth by his power,
\par The One who established the productive land by his wisdom
\par And who stretched out the heavens by his understanding.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af25 \ltrch\fcs0 \f1\cf23\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033\langfenp1033\insrsid9976433 16}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af25 \ltrch\fcs0 \f1\cf25\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033\langfenp1033\insrsid9976433 \~When he makes his voice heard,
\par The waters in the heavens are in turmoil,
\par And he causes clouds to ascend from the ends of the earth.
\par He makes lightning for the rain,
\par And he brings the wind out of his storehouses.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af25 \ltrch\fcs0 \f1\cf23\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033\langfenp1033\insrsid9976433 17}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af25 \ltrch\fcs0 \f1\cf25\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033\langfenp1033\insrsid9976433 \~Every man acts unreasonably and without knowledge.

\par Every metalworker will be put to shame because of the carved image;
\par For his metal image is a falsehood,
\par And there is no spirit in them.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af25 \ltrch\fcs0 \f1\cf23\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033\langfenp1033\insrsid9976433 18}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af25 \ltrch\fcs0 \f1\cf25\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033\langfenp1033\insrsid9976433 \~They are a delusion, a work of mockery.
\par When their day of reckoning comes, they will perish.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af25 \ltrch\fcs0 \f1\cf23\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033\langfenp1033\insrsid9976433 19}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af25 \ltrch\fcs0 \f1\cf25\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033\langfenp1033\insrsid9976433 \~The Share of Jacob is not like these things,
\par For he is the One who formed everything,
